{
  "stem": "15962.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "The camp, which was a converted army barrack, and is now serving again for-- for the Austrian Garrison overlooked the Danube-- or-- or sorry, overlooked the valley of the Danube.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And by that time, we could see daily air raids by silver, large bombers that would be visible, high in the sky.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But even more impressive were the British fighter planes that would suddenly swoop on transports of trains-- the train line was visible from the camp.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And they would actually precede the sirens.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They would suddenly arrive before the sirens were able to sound.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And that was some grief for us to see all the trains that were bringing refugees from-- I mean, inhabitants from Vienna, trying to escape the Russian advance.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I had also a job as an orderly, standing next to the main gate.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And that was very unpleasant, because I had to watch the shifts going in and out and saw the suffering people, from close proximity.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know, no idea.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, we were not in contact with the Austrian population.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the German guards, I would say that they were beastly till the very end and never changed their attitude towards the prisoners.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were in-- in Melk about two months.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And probably because of the advancing front from the east, we were then again shipped westward, towards Mauthausen.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was our second arrival in Mauthausen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This time it was getting extremely crowded.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And after a few nights in the main camp, we were pushed to a hastily erected tent camp, which consisted of several almost circus tents, large tents, that were on a slope during the rainy season.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the constant rains were just flooding the place.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was no dry place to be.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
